Class VoidParameterServerStressTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nd4j.parameterserver.distributed.VoidParameterServerStressTest

  • public class VoidParameterServerStressTest
extends java.lang.Object
    This set of tests doesn't has any assertions within. All we care about here - performance and availability Tests for all environments are paired: one test for blocking messages, other one for non-blocking messages.
